    <hasSideEffectDescription>unusually high number of eosinophils (type of white blood cell) in blood; High number of eosinophils crowd at specific areas of the body, causing medical conditions linked to inflammation that can affecti multiple areas of the body.</hasSideEffectDescription>
  </rdf:Description>
