    <hasClinicalEffects>None specifically reported in the dedicated drug interaction study.</hasClinicalEffects>
    <hasInteractionDescription>Concurrent use of warfarin and azithromycin may potentiate the effects of oral anticoagulants.</hasInteractionDescription>
