    <rdfs:label>ITN261</rdfs:label>
    <hasClinicalEffects>Not Specified</hasClinicalEffects>
    <hasInteractionDescription>The action of sulfonamides may be antagonized by paminobenzoic acid and its derivatives, particularly potassium aminobenzoate and the procaine group of local anesthetics.</hasInteractionDescription>
