    <rdfs:label>ITN240</rdfs:label>
    <hasClinicalEffects>Concomitant administration of probenecid reportedly increases Cmax and AUC of cefixime and decreases renal clearance and volume of distribution of the drug.</hasClinicalEffects>
    <hasInteractionDescription>Concomitant administration of probenecid reportedly increases Cmax and AUC of cefixime and decreases renal clearance and volume of distribution of the drug.</hasInteractionDescription>
