    <hasStewardshipDescription>Store Nitrofurantoin at temperatures not exceeding 30°C. Keep it in a dry place away from direct heat and moisture. Proper storage ensures that the medicine remains stable and effective until its expiration date.</hasStewardshipDescription>
  </rdf:Description>
